    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are consistent with the MRL 2 assessment plan per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The CFD model is judged credible for the stated COU: identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device using the relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1). No weakeners were identified that would reduce confidence below the required threshold.",
